description: This dazzling truck is bringing the best cuisines of the world straight to the streets of Detroit, and everyone is finding the food from Chef in a Box to be amazingly delicious.  Their eclectic menu includes favorites from American, Mexican, and Middle Eastern fare, like their Bacon & Cheddar Burger (⅓ lb beef patty, topped with hickory smoked bacon, yummy melted cheddar, and all the rest of the best burger fixings), the Battered Fish Tacos (batter-fried cod, shredded cabbage blend, tangy pico de gallo, cilantro- lime sauce, within a grilled flour tortilla), and Chicken Shawarma (juicy grilled chicken breast, pickle, and garlic sauce, all in a warm tortilla). For all this and much more, come on up to the Chef in a Box (or call on this truck to cater your next event), and indulge in the tastiest bang for your buck.
name: Chef In A Box
